<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:13:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>海地冲突导致数千人陷入饥荒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/haiti-conflict-drives-thousands-toward-famine-2024-10-01/</link><description>近几个月来，海地因帮派引发的社会和政治危机导致遭受严重饥饿的人数不断增加，估计有 540 万海地人已经耗尽了食物，并且一天或更长时间没有进食。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 00:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/haiti-conflict-drives-thousands-toward-famine-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>全球投资者呼吁撤离中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-investors-call-time-their-exodus-china-2024-09-30/</link><description>全球投资者正准备再次押注中国，这是北京努力扭转经济放缓并重振股市长期兴趣引发的重大情绪转变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-investors-call-time-their-exodus-china-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜批评美国在韩国部署核资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-criticises-us-deployment-nuclear-assets-south-korea-2024-09-30/</link><description>据朝鲜官方媒体朝中社周二报道，朝鲜国防部谴责美国在韩国部署核战略资产，当时首尔正在为庆祝建军节举行罕见的阅兵式做准备。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-criticises-us-deployment-nuclear-assets-south-korea-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：鲍威尔慎重，中国为第四季度开盘奠定了基础</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 21:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>马赫雷斯进球让阿赫利在亚冠联赛中保持完美</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</link><description>沙特阿拉伯的阿赫利队周一在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中保持了完美的开局，里亚德·马赫雷斯和罗杰·伊巴内斯的进球帮助球队以 2-0 战胜了阿尔瓦斯尔队，而克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多则在阿尔纳赛尔队以 2-1 战胜阿尔-瓦斯尔队的比赛中进球。雷扬。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 20:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国的激励措施吸引了谨慎的电动汽车买家，特斯拉的季度交付量将上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</link><description>华尔街估计，在全球最大汽车市场中国的长期激励措施和利润丰厚的融资计划的推动下，特斯拉周三第三季度电动汽车交付量预计将增长 8%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>科学家解释珠穆朗玛峰的异常生长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</link><description>珠穆朗玛峰是地球上最高的山峰，海拔 8.85 公里（5.5 英里），而且实际上还在不断增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>研究小组向铜多头发出了一条发人深省的信息：Andy Home</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/study-group-has-sobering-message-copper-bulls-andy-home-2024-09-30/</link><description>由于中国承诺的经济刺激计划重新点燃了投资者的热情，本周铜价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/study-group-has-sobering-message-copper-bulls-andy-home-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>北京放宽购房规定以刺激需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-eases-home-purchase-rules-boost-demand-2024-09-30/</link><description>继上海和深圳采取类似举措后，北京周一放松了购房限制，以提振需求并支撑陷入困境的房地产市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-eases-home-purchase-rules-boost-demand-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国联邦贸易委员会允许雪佛龙-赫斯交易，但禁止约翰·赫斯加入董事会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ftc-allows-chevron-hess-deal-bars-john-hess-board-2024-09-30/</link><description>美国联邦贸易委员会周一允许雪佛龙以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司 (Hess Corp)，该命令禁止赫斯公司首席执行官约翰·赫斯 (John Hess) 进入雪佛龙董事会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ftc-allows-chevron-hess-deal-bars-john-hess-board-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟表示即使在关税之后仍可能继续与中国进行电动汽车谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</link><description>欧盟一位高级官员周一表示，即使在征收关税之后，欧盟委员会仍愿意继续与中国就避免对中国电动汽车征收关税的潜在协议进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌入股市，担心错过史诗般的反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国股市的动物精神又回来了，投资者在北京的政策刺激下纷纷涌入股市，担心错过一些人认为的历史性反弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国“具有里程碑意义”的消费刺激计划后，痛苦的政策选择迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国的刺激计划旨在填补消费者的口袋，以实现其2024年的增长目标，这打破了几十年前的政策剧本，但让家庭需求而不是投资成为发展的可持续驱动力是一条充满艰难选择的漫长道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>刺激措施助推中国股市创2008年以来最大单日涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</link><description>随着投资者争先恐后地加入北京最新一系列刺激措施引发的强劲反弹，国内 A 股成交量创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的运行将黄金推向四年来最好的季度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-pulls-back-dovish-fed-sets-it-best-quarter-since-2016-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一金价下跌，在美国货币宽松和中东紧张局势加剧推动历史性上涨后稍作喘息，这使得黄金有望迎来 2020 年以来最好的季度表现。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:52:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-pulls-back-dovish-fed-sets-it-best-quarter-since-2016-2024-09-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>